hadiths[48]{hadithnumber,text}:
2688,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai, tum jannat mein dakhil nahin ho saktey jab tak ke tum ( sahih manon mein) momin na bin jaao aur tum momin nahin ho saktey jab tak ke tum aapas main eik doosrey sey) sachi ( mohabbat na karney lago. kya main tumhen eik aisi chiz na bataaun ke agar tum usey karney lago to tum mein bahami (aapsi) mohabbat paida ho jaey ( wo ye ke) aapas mein salam ko aam karo) phailao ( '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Salam , Shureh bin Haani an abih, Abdullah bin Amr , Bara , Anas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2689,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : (السلام عليكم)‏‏‏‏ Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''( uskey liye ( das nekiyan hain'' , phir eik doosra shakhs aaya aur usney kaha : السلام عليكم ورحمة الله padhi. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( uskey liye ( bees nekiyan hain'' , phir eik aur aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : « السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته » , padhi. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( uskey liye ( tees nekiyan hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali, abu-Saeed aur Sehal bin Hanif sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2690,"abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey unkey paas hazir honey ki ijazat talab ki to unhoney kaha : « السلام عليكم » kya main andar aa sakta hun? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( dil mein) kaha : abhi to eik baar ijazat talab ki hai, thodi der khamosh reh kar phir unhoney kaha : « السلام عليكم » kya main andar aa sakta hun? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( dil mein) kaha : abhi to do hi baar ijazat talab ki hai. thodi der ( mazeed ( khamosh reh kar unhoney phir kaha : « السلام عليكم » kya mujhey andar dakhil honey ki ijazat hai? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( dil mein kaha ( teen baar ijazat talab kar chukey , phir abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) wapis ho liye , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney darbaan sey kaha : abu-Musa ney kya kya ? usney kaha : lot gaey . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha unhen bula kar merey paas laao , phir jab wo unkey paas aaye to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ye aap ney kya kya hai? unhoney kaha : mainey sunnat par amal kya hai, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha sunnat par ? qism Allah ki ! tumhen uskey sunnat honey par daleel o sabut pesh karna hoga warna main tumharey sath sakht bartaaw karunga. abu Saeed Khudri kehtey hain : phir wo hamarey paas aaye, us waqt hum ansaar ki eik jamaat key sath they. abu-Musa Ash-ari ney kaha : aey ansaar ki jamaat ! kya tum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees ko doosrey logon sey ziyada janney waley nahin ho, kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye nahin farmaya : « الاستئذان ثلاث » ( ijazat talbi) teen baar hai. agar tumhen ijazat dey di jaey to ghar mein jaao aur agar ijazat na di jaey to lot jaao? ( ye sun kar) log un sey hansi mazaq karney lagey , abu Saeed Khudri kehtey hain : mainey apna sar abu-Musa Ash-ari ki taraf ooncha kar key kaha : is silsiley mein jo bhi saza aap ko milegi main is mein hissedaar hunga, Raavi kehtey hain : phir wo (abu-Saeed) umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye, aur unko is hadees ki khabar di, umr ney kaha : mujhey is hadees ka ilm nahin tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur Jariri ka naam Saeed bin Ayas hai aur un ki kunniyat abu-Masood hai. ye hadees unkey siwa aur logon ney bhi abu-Nazara sey riwayat ki hai, aur abu-Nazara Abdi ka naam Munzir bin Malik bin Qataa hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali aur Saad ki azad karda laundi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2691,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aap key paas aaney ki teen baar ijazat maangi , to aap ney mujhey ijazat dey di . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- abu-Zameel ka naam Samak Hanafi hai, 3- merey nazdik umr ko abu-Musa ki is baat par aetraz aur inkar us wajeh sey tha ke abu-Musa ney bayan kya ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ijazat teen baar talab ki jaey, agar ijazat mil jaey to theek warna lot jao''. (reh gaya umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka apna maamla ( to unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey teen baar ijazat talab ki thi to unhen ijazat mil gaee thi, is hadees ki khabar unhen nahin thi jisey abu-Musa ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aap ney farmaya : ''phir agar andar janey ki ijazat mil jaey to theek warna wapis lot jaao ''."
2692,"eik shakhs masjid mein aaya (us waqt ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam masjid key eik koney mein tashrif farma they. usney namaz padhi phir aa kar aap ko salam arz kya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya « وعليك » '' tum par bhi salam ho, jaao dobara namaz padho kyonkey tum ney namaz nahin padhi '', phir Raavi ney puri hadees bayan ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney ye hadees Ubedullah bin umr sey aur Ubedullah bin umr ney Saeed Maqbari sey riwayat ki hai, is mein unhoney « an Abeeh an abi Hurera » kaha hai, is mein « فسلم عليه وقال وعليك » '' usney aap ko salam kya aur aap ney kaha tum par bhi salam ho '' ka zikr nahin kya, 3- Yahya bin Saeed ki hadees ziyada sahih hai."
2693,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : '' Jibreel tumhen salam kehtey hain, to unhoney jawab mein kaha : (وعلیہ السلام ورحمۃ اللہ وبرکاتہ) un par bhi salam aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkaten hun '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein bani Numer key eik shakhs sey bhi riwayat hai wo apney baap sey aur wo unkey dada key wastey sey riwayat kartey hain, 3- Zohri ney bhi ye hadees abu-Salma key wastey sey Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai."
2694,"puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! jab do aadmi aapas mein milen to salam karney mein pehal kon karey ? aap ney farmaya : '' un dono mein sey jo Allah key ziyada qarib hai'' padhi. .) wo pehal kerega (Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ابوفروہ رہاوی مقارب الحدیث hain, magar unkey betey Muhammad bin Yazeed un sey munkar hadisein riwayat kartey hain."
2695,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin hai jo hamarey gheron sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar kerey. na Yahud ki mushaabihat karo aur na Nasara ki, yahudiyon ka salam ungliyon ka ishara hai aur Nasara ka salam hatheliyon ka ishara hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad zaeef hai, 2- ibne-Mubarak ney ye hadees ibne-Lahiaa sey riwayat ki hai, aur usey unhoney marfoo nahin kya hai."
2696,"main Sabit Bunani key sath ja raha tha, wo bachon key paas sey guzrey to unhen salam kya, Sabit ney (apna waqia bayan kartey huye ( kaha : main Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key sath ( ja raha ( tha wo bachon key paas sey guzrey to unhoney salam kya, phir Anas ney ( apna waqia bayan kartey huye ( kaha : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha, aap bachon key paas sey guzrey to unhen salam kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- usey kaee logon ney Sabit sey riwayat kya hai, 3- ye hadees mutaaddid sanadon sey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai."
2697,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik din masjid mein guzrey wahan aurton ki eik jamaat bethi hui thi, chunanche aap ney unhen apney haath key isharay sey salam kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- abdul-Hameed ( Raavi ( ney bhi pattey haath sey ishara kya (ke is tarah ( , 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : Shehar bin Hoshab key wastey sey Abdul-Humed bin Behram ki riwayat mein koi harj nahin hai, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Shehar hasanul-hadees hain aur in ko riwayat hadees mein qawi Bukhari kehtey hain : unkey barey mein ibn Aun ney kalam kya hai. ibn Aun kehtey hain : « إن شهرا نزكوه » key wastey sey kaha : shehar ki shakhsiyat ko muhaddeseen ney daghdaar bataya hai. abu-Daawood kehtey hain ke nazar kehtey hain « نزكوه » ka matlab ye hai ke « طعنوا فيه » yani un ki shakhsiyat ko dagh daar bataya hai, aur logon ney un par jireh isliye ki hai ke wo sultan (hukoomat) key mulaazim ban gaey hain."
2698,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''betey! jab tum apney ghar walon key paas jaao to unhen salam kya karo, ye salam tumharey liye aur tumharey ghar walon key liye khair o barkat ka baais hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2699,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' baat cheet shuru karney sey pehley salam kya karo ''
2700,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Yahud o Nasara ko salam karney mein pehal na karo, aur jab tumhari unkey kisi fard sey raastey mein mulaqat ho jaey to usey tang raastey sey hi janey par majbur karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2701,"kuchh yahudiyon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : « السّام عليك » ''tum par maut aur halakat aaye'' ,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jawab mein farmaya : « عليكم », Aaisha ney (is par do lafz badha kar) kaha « بل عليكم السام واللعنة »'' balke tum par halakat aur lanat ho.'' Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! Allah Taala har mamley mein narmi, naram rawi aur mulaaimiyat ko pasand karta hai.''  Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : kya aap ney suna nahin? unhoney kya kaha hai?  aap ney farmaya : ''tabhi to mainey « عليكم » kaha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Basra Ghifaari, ibne-Umar , Anas aur abu-Abdur-Rehman Juhni sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2702,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik aisi majlis key paas sey guzrey jis mein musalman aur Yahud dono they to aap ney unhen salam kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2703,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sawar pedal chalney waley ko aur pedal chalney wala bethey huye ko , aur thodey log ziyada logon ko (yani chhoti jamaat badi jamaat ko salam karey).'' aur ibne Musanna ney apni riwayat mein itna izafa kiya hai : ''chhota apney badey ko salam karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- Ayub Sakhtiyaan , Yunus bin Ubaid aur Ali bin Yazeed kehtey hain ke Hasan Basri ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai. 3- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Shabal , Fazala bin Ubaid aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2704,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''chhota badey ko , chalney wala bethey huye ko aur thodey log ziyada logon ko salam karen.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2705,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sawar pedal chalney waley ko aur chalney wala khadey huye shakhs ko aur thodey log ziyada logon ko salam karen.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2706,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi shakhs kisi majlis mein pahunchey to salam karey , phir agar uska dil bethney ko chahey to beth jaey. phir jab uth kar janey lagey to salam karey. pehla (salam) doosrey  (salam) sey ziyada zaruri nahin hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees ibne Ajlan sey bhi aai hai, ibne Ajlan ney basanad « Saeed Al Maqbari an Abeeh an abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam» riwayat ki hai."
2707,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(ghar mein dakhil honey ki) ijazat milney sey pehley hi jisney (darwazey ka ( parda khiska kar kisi key ghar key andar jhaankaa , aur ghar waley ki biwi ki parda dari ki to usney eik aisa kaam kiya jiska karna uskey liye halal na tha, jis waqt usney apni nigah andar dali thi kaash! us waqt uska saamna kisi aisey shakhs sey ho jata jo uski dono aankhen phod deta to main is par usey khoon-bahaa  na deta. aur agar koi shakhs aisey darwazey key samney sey guzra jis par koi parda pada huwa nahin hai aur darwaza band bhi nahin hai phir uski nazar uth gaee to uski kuchh khata nahin. ghalati aur kotahi to ghar waley ki hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum is tarah ki hadees sirf ibne-Lahiaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur abu-Umama Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2708,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney ghar mein they (usi doran) eik shakhs ney aap key ghar mein jhaankaa , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam teer ka phal ley kar lapkey (ke uski aankhen phod den) lekin wo fauran peechhey hat gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2709,"eik shakhs ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key hujrey main eik surakh sey jhaankaa (us waqt) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key haath main eik lakdi thi jis sey aap apna sar khujaa rahey they. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar mujhey (pehley sey) malum hota ke to jhank raha hai to main isey teri aankh mein ghop deta (tujhey pata nahin) ijazat maangney ka hukm to dekhney key sabab hi sey hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2710,"Safwan bin Umayya ney unhen doodh, pewsi aur kakdi key tukdey dey kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bheja aur aap us waqt Makka key oonchaai waley hissey mein they, main aap key paas ijazat liye aur salam kiye baghair chala gaya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wapis bahar jaao, phir kaho (السلام علیکم ( kya main andar aa sakta hun?'' ye us waqt ki baat hai jab Safwan Islam la chukey they. Amr bin Abdullah kehtey hain : ye hadees Umayya bin Safwan ney mujh sey bayan ki hai lekin unhoney ye nahin kaha ke ye hadees mainey Kalda sey suni hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- isey hum sirf ibne-Jurej ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain. 3- abu-Aasim ney bhi ibne-Jurej sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
2711,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik qarz key silsiley mein jo merey walid key zimme tha kuchh baat karney key liye aap key paas hazir honey ki ijazat maangi to aap ney kaha : ''kon hai?'' mainey kaha : main hun, aap ney farmaya : ''main main (kya hai)?''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2712,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon ko safar sey raat mein biwiyon key paas lot kar aaney sey roka hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Anas , ibne-Umar , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon ko raat mein biwiyon key paas safar sey wapis lot kar aaney sey roka ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key is rokney key bawajud do shakhs raat mein lot kar apni biwiyon key paas aaye (nateeja unhen us nafarmani ka ye mila) ke un dono mein sey har eik ney apni biwi key paas eik doosrey mard ko paya."
2713,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi tehreer likhey to likhney key baad is par mitti dalna chahiye, kyonkey us sey hajat  poori karne ki ziyada tawaqqo hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees munkir hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey abu-Zubair ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- Hamza hamarey nazdik Amr Naseebi key betey hain, aur wo hadees bayan karney mein zaeef maaney jatey hain."
2714,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahuncha. aap key samney eik kaatib betha huwa tha. mainey suna aap us sey farma rahey they : ''tum apna qalam apney kaan par rakhey raha karo kyonkey is sey likhwaane walon ko aagaahi aur yad dahani ho jaya kereygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain aur ye sanad zaeef hai. 2- Anbasaa bin Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad bin Azan , dono hadees bayan karney mein zaeef qarar diye gaey hain."
2715,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey hukm diya ke main aap key liye Yahud ki kuchh tehreer seekh lun , aap ney farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! main Yahud ki tehreer par aitimad aur itminan nahin karta.''  chunanche abhi aadha mahina bhi nahin guzra tha ke mainey aap key liye usey seekh liya. kehtey hain : phir jab mainey seekh liya aur aap ko yahudiyon key paas kuch likh kar bhejna huwa to mainey likh kar unkey paas bhej diya, aur jab yahudiyon ney koi chiz likh kar aap key paas bheji to mainey un ki kitab (tehreer) padh kar aap ko suna di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa bhi dusri sanad sey Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, isey Aamash ney Sabit bin Ubaid Ansari key wastey sey Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main siryaani zaban seekh lun."
2716,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni wafat sey pehley Kisraa aur Qaisar, Najashi aur sarey sarkash o mutakabbir baadshaahon ko Allah ki taraf dawat detey huye khutoot likh kar bhejey. us Najaashi sey wo Najaashi (badshah habsh As'hama) murad nahin hai ke jinkey intiqal par Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney namaze janaza padhi thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2717,"Abu-Sufiyaan bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey bayan kiya ke wo Quraish key kuchh taajiron key sath Sham mein they ke Hiraql (shahanshaah Shaam) ney unhen bula bheja , to wo sab uskey paas aaye, phir Sufiyan ney aagey baat badhaai. kaha : phir usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka khat mangwaayaa. phir khat padha gaya, is mein likha tha : (بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم من محمد عبدالله ورسوله إلى هرقل عظيم الروم السلام على من اتبع الهدى أمابعد) ''main shuru karta hun us Allah key naam sey jo rahmaan ( bada meharban (aur Rahim ( nihayat reham karney wala ( hai. ye khat Muhammad ki janib sey hai jo Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. aur Hiraql key paas bheja ja raha hai jo Rom key shahanshaah hain. salamti hai us shakhs key liye jo hidayat ki perwi karey (امابعد): hamd aur naat key baad … aakhir tak.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- abu-Sufiyaan ka naam Sakhr bin Harab (Raziallahu anhu) tha."
2718,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab ajmi (ghair arabi) (baadshaahon) ko khutoot bhejney ka irada farmaya to aap ko bataya gaya ke ajmi baghair mohar laga huwa khat qubul nahin kartey chunanche aap ney (mohar key liye) eik angoothi banwaai, to un main aap ki hatheli mein uski chamak ko is waqt dekh raha hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2719,"main aur merey do dost (Madina) aaye, faqr (ghareebi) aur faaqe aur sakhti aur mashaqqat ki bina par hamari sama'at (sun'ne ki salahiyat) mutassir ho gaee thi padhi. aur hamari aankhen dhans gaee thin, hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba key samney apney aap ko pesh karney lagey lekin hamein kisi ney qubul na kiya padhi. , phir hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaey to aap hamein apney ghar ley aaye, us waqt aap key paas teen bakriyan thin. aap ney farmaya : ''un ka doodh hum sab key liye doho.''  to hum dohtey aur har shakhs apna hissa peeta aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka hissa utha kar rakh detey, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat mein tashrif latey aur is andaz sey salam kartey they ke soney wala jaag na uthey aur jaagney wala sun bhi ley, phir aap masjid aatey namaze tahajjud padhtey phir ja kar apney hissey ka doodh peetey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2720,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko us waqt salam kiya jab aap peshab kar rahey they, to aap ney uskey salam ka jawab nahin diya."
2721,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey milna chahta tha, magar aap tak pahunch na saka , main betha raha phir kuchh log samney aaye jin mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi they. mein aap sey waqif na tha, aap un logon mein suleh safai kara rahey they, jab aap (us kaam sey) farigh huye to aap key sath kuchh doosrey log bhi uth khadey huye, un logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! jab mainey ( logon ko) aisa kehtey dekha to mainey kaha : ''(!علیک السلام یا رسول اللہ)'' (aap par salamti ho aey Allah key Rasool) aur aisa mainey teen baar kaha , aap ney farmaya : '' « علیک السلام » maiyat ka salam hai''  aap ney bhi aisa teen baar kaha , phir aap meri taraf puri tarah mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : ''jab aadmi apney musalman bhai sey miley to uskey liye munasib ye hai ke kahey (Assalamualaikum Warahmatullah) phir aap ney merey salam ka jawab is tarah lotaya , farmaya : (وعلیک ورحمة اللہ وعلیک ورحمة اللہ وعلیک ورحمة اللہ) (teen baar). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu Ghifaar ney ye hadees basanad :(ابو تمیمہ الہجیمی an ابی جری جابر بن سلیم الہجیمی) sey riwayat ki hai, Hajeemi kehtey hain : main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya phir aagey puri hadees bayan kar di. abu Tameema ka naam Tareef bin Majaalid hai."
2722,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , phir aap sey arz kiya : « علیک السلام » aap par salamti ho to aap ney farmaya : « علیک السلام » mat kaho balke « السلام علیک » kaho aur aagey pura lamba qissa bayan kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2723,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab salam kartey to teen baar salam kartey aur jab koi baat kehtey to usey teen baar dohraate. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. faeyda padhi. : taake baat achchhi tarah samajh mein aa jaey.
2724,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam masjid mein tashrif farma they, aap key sath log bhi bethey they, usi doran achcha teen aadmi aaye , un mein sey do Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf badh aaye , aur eik wapis chala gaya, jab wo dono Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunch kar rukey to unhoney salam kiya, phir un dono mein sey eik ney majlis mein kuchh jagah ( gunjaaish ( dekhi to wo usi mein) ghus kar) beth gaya. aur doosra shakhs un logon key (yani Sahaba) key peechhey ja kar beth gaya. aur teesra to peeth modey chala hi gaya tha, phir jab farigh huye to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Sahaba ko mukhatib kar key farmaya : ''kya main tumhen teeno shkhason key mutalliq na bataaun? (suno) un mein sey eik ney Allah ki panah hasil ki to Allah ney usey panah di aur doosrey ney sharam ki to Allah ney bhi us sey sharam ki aur raha teesra shakhs to usney aeraz kiya (bachna chaaha), chunanche Allah ney bhi us sey aeraz kiya (bachna chaaha), munh pher liya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- abu Murra Umme-Haani binte abi Talib (Raziallahu Anha) key azad karda ghulam hain aur unka naam Yazeed hai, ye bhi kaha jata hai ke wo Aqeel ibne-Abi Talib key azad karda ghulam hain."
2725,hum jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aatey to jis ko jahan jagah milti wahin beth jata. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Zuhair bin Muawiya ney Simaak sey bhi riwayat ki hai.
2726,"(sanad mein is baat ki sarahat hai ke Abu-Is'haq ney Bara sey suna nahin hai isliye sanad mein taalluq khatam hai, lekin gawahi ki binaa par sahih hai, khaas-taur se Shoba ki riwayat honey ki wajeh sey qawi hai) ansaar key kuchh log raastey mein bethey huye they aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka unkey paas sey guzar huwa to aap ney un sey farmaya : ''(yun to raastey mein bethna achchha nahin hai) lekin agar tum bethna zaruri samajhtey ho to salam ka jawab diya karo, mazloom ki madad kiya karo, aur (bhooley bhatkey huye ko) raasta bata diya karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur abu-Shuraih Khuzai Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2727,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab do musalman aapas main eik doosrey sey miltey aur) salam (aur musaafa kartey hain to un dono key eik doosrey sey alehda aur juda honey sey pehley unhen bakhsh diya jata hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Bara sey mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
2728,"eik aadmi ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! hamara aadmi apney bhai sey ya apney dost sey milta hai to kya wo uskey samney jhukey? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin''  usney puchha : kya wo us sey chimat jaey aur uska bosa ley? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin''  usney kaha : phir to wo uska haath pakdey aur musaafa karey, aap ney farmaya : ''haan'' (bas itna hi kafi hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2729,mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba mein musaafe ka riwaaj tha? unhoney kaha : haan. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2730,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mukammal salam ((السلام علیکم ورحمة اللہ وبرکاتہ) kehney key sath sath) haath ko haath mein lena yani (musaafa karna) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yahya bin sulaim ki riwayat sey jisey wo Sufiyan sey riwayat kartey hain jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key mutalliq puchha to unhoney isey mehfooz shumar nahin kiya, aur kaha ke merey nazdik Yahya bin Sulaim ney Sufiyan ki wo riwayat murad li hai jisey unhoney Mansoor sey riwayat ki hai, aur Mansoor ney Khaisma sey aur Khaisma ney us sey jisney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai aur ibne-Masood ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. aap ney farmaya : ''(baad namaze Isha) baat cheet aur qissa-goi nahin karni chahiye, siwaye us shakhs key jisko (abhi kuchh der baad uth kar tahajjud ki) namaz padhni hai ya safar karna hai, Muhammad kehtey hain : aur Mansoor sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Abu-Is'haq sey aur Abu-Is'haq ney Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed sey ya unkey siwa kisi aur sey riwayat ki hai. wo kehtey hain : salam ki takmil sey murad haath pakadna (musaafa karna) hai. 3- is bab mein Bara aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2731,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mareez ki mukammal iyaadat ye hai ke tum mein sey iyaadat karney wala apna haath uski peshani par rakhey'' ,ya aap ney ye farmaya : ''(Raavi ko shubha ho gaya hai) apna haath uskey haath par rakhey, phir us sey puchhey ke wo kaisa hai? aur tumharey salam ki takmil ye hai ke tum aapas main eik doosrey sey musaafa karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Ubedullah bin Zahr Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur Ali bin Yazeed zaeef hain. 3- Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman ki kunniyat abu-Abdur-Rehman hai aur ye Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid bin Yazeed bin Muawiya key azad karda ghulam hain aur Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur Qasim Shaami hain."
2732,"Zaid bin Harisa Madina aaye (us waqt) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey ghar mein tashrif farma they, wo aap key paas aaye aur darwaza khatkhataayaa , to aap un ki taraf nangey badan apney kapdey samet'te huye lapkey aur qism Allah ki mainey aap ko nangey badan na is sey pehley kabhi dekha tha aur na uskey baad dekha padhi. , aap ney (badh kar) unhen galey laga liya aur unka bosa liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Zohri ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2733,"eik Yahudi ney apney sathi sey kaha : chalo us Nabi key paas ley chaltey hain. uskey sathi ney kaha ''Nabi'' na kaho. warna agar unhoney sun liya to un ki chaar aankhen ho jaeyngi, phir wo dono Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , aur aap sey (Musa (Alaihissalam) ko di gaeen) nau khuli hui nishaniyon key mutalliq poochha. aap ney un sey kaha :(1) kisi ko Allah ka shareek na banao. (2) chori na karo. (3) zina na karo. (4) nahaq kisi ko qatl na karo. (5) kisi begunaah ko haakim key samney na ley jaao ke wo usey qatl kar dey. (6) jadu na karo. (7) sood mat khaao. (8) paarsaa aurat par zina ki tohmat mat lagaao. (9) aur dushman sey muqabley key din peeth pher kar bhagney ki koshish na karo. aur khas tum yahudiyon key liye ye baat hai ke « sabt » ( saneechar ( key silsiley mein had sey aagey na badho, (aap ka jawab sun kar) unhoney aap key haath pair chuma aur kaha : hum gawahi detey hain ke aap Nabi hain. aap ney farmaya : ''phir tumhen meri perwi karney sey kya chiz rokti hai?'' unhoney kaha : Dawud (Alaihissalam) ney apney Rab sey dua ki thi ke un ki aulad mein hamesha koi Nabi rahey. isliye hum dartey hain ke agar hamney aap ki ittiba (perwi) ki to Yahudi hamen maar dalengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Yazeed bin Aswad , ibne-Umar aur Kaab bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2734,"Fateh Makka waley saal mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaee. aap us waqt ghusl farma rahey they, aur Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) eik kapdey sey aap ko aad kiye huye thin. mainey salam kiya to aap ney puchha : ''kon hain ye '' mainey kaha : main Umme-Haani hun, aap ney farmaya : ''Umme-Haani ka aana Mubarak ho.'' Raavi kehtey hain phir abu Murra ney hadees ka pura waqia bayan kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2735,"jab main (Makka sey Madina hijrat kar key) aaya to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''muhaajir sawar ka aana Mubarak ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad sahih nahin hai. hum isey sirf Musa bin Masood ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Sufiyan sey riwayat kartey hain. Musa bin Masood hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain. 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney bhi ye hadees Sufiyan sey aur Sufiyan ney Abu-Is'haq sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. aur is sanad mein Musab bin Saad ka zikr nahin kiya hai aur yehi sahih tar hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Bashaar ko kehtey huye suna : Musa bin Masood hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain. 4- Muhammad bin Bashaar kehtey hain : mainey Musa bin Masood sey bahut si hadisein lein, phir mainey un sey hadisein leni chhod di. 5- is bab mein Barida , ibne-Abbas aur abu-Juhaifa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
